casebody.data:
Frederic C. SCHULTZ, Petitioner,
v.
John G. ROBERTS, Jr., Chief Justice, Supreme Court of the United States, et al. No. 19-275 Supreme Court of the United States. October 15, 2019 Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Ninth Circuit denied. The Chief Justice took no part in the consideration or decision of this petition.
